changes.description: Added a user to the test data to enable e2e tests. Since those rely on a real Firebase user, a user with a real Firebase ID (as opposed to the fake ones we use in tests) needed to be added to the test data.

Deleted unneeded environment variables from the CI yaml file. The database URL variables were previously used to set up the database, but now that it's set using a credentials file, they're no longer needed and should've been removed.
